        "subject": "LU-2456 lnet: Dynamic LNet Configuration (DLC) Feature",
        "message": "LU-2456 lnet: Dynamic LNet Configuration (DLC) Feature\n\nThis is the first patch of a set of patches that enables DLC.\n\nThis patch adds the following features to LNET.  Currently these\nfeatures are not driven by user space.\n- Enabling Routing on Demand\n- Adjusting router buffer pools\n- Adding/deleting routes dynamically\n- Adding/Deleting Networks dynamically\n\nSigned-off-by: Amir Shehata <amir.shehata@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I134c8a717c2ab77ef916d16237b456b9505bbd7b\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
